<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.7">
<l>vāṉava rāti yeṉkō vāṉavar teyva meṉkō</l>
<l>vāṉavar pōka meṉkō vāṉavar muṟṟu meṉkō</l>
<l>vūṉamil celva meṉkō vūṉamil cuvarkka meṉkō</l>
<l>vūṉamiṉ mōkka meṉkō voḷimaṇi vaṇṇa ṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I say “first of the celestials”? Will I say “god the the celestials”?</l>
<l>Will I say “enjyoment of the celestials”? Will I say “the all of the celestials”?</l>
<l>Will I say “flawless wealth”? Will I say “flawless heaven”?</l>
<l>Will I say “flawless liberation”? – to the one of bright sapphire colour.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
